{"type": "article", "id": 17706, "title": "吴冠中系列纹样餐具", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-18T06:40:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122732LHY1NTqobu5QFl7r.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t成立于 2014 年 9 月的造作很喜欢使用色彩，这是他们独立出来的设计团队 Z-Inhouse 推出的吴冠中系列纹样餐具。有红色和黄色两组，分别使用了吴冠中的《印尼舟群》和《白桦林》两幅画作纹样，陶瓷碗里面装饰以明媚鲜艳的红色和黄色，富有非常强烈的艺术气息。售价 199 元起，<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/item/300050\" target=\"_blank\">这里分别是红色款</a>和<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/item/300054\" target=\"_blank\">黄色款的购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144801ujsHFXPJ7bIQz5DE.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144802bQsuyc5i9PmC4lNq.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144802XrcgatxvQCG6MEZW.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144803rYbqEa9TXD05Lmci.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261448055EU3JITQo2XahkYL.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}